2005-01-11  Neal H. Walfield  <neal@gnu.org>

	* Makefile.am (deva_SOURCES): Remove physmem-user.h and
	physmem-user.c.
	(deva_LDADD): Add ../libhurd-btree/libhurd-btree.a and
